                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7587" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0347</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2610 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破茧成蝶：安徽中航显示组织变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking the cocoon into a butterfly:  The road to organizational change for Anhui AVIC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伍章俊，袁烨，马晓萌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合肥工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽中航显示技术有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；跨部门矩阵式组织结构；复合高适型组织结构；安徽中航显示；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organizational change, cross-departmental matrix organizational structure, composite high-adaptability organizational structure, Anhui AVIC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革是一个阶段性的过程，通过有目的、有计划地改变组织的内在结构和行为方式，以应对内外部环境的变化，促使组织达到新的平衡状态，更好地实现组织目标。本案例描述了安徽中航显示技术有限公司在面对特种装备许可政策连续消减的不利环境时，审时度势、谋求变革、持续改革组织结构的过程。为适应市场需求的变化，安徽中航显示将原有的独立职能型组织结构转变为跨部门矩阵式组织结构，以实现更好的协同效应；随后，为进一步激发员工的积极性和创造性，又将跨部门矩阵式组织结构进一步演进为复合高适应性组织结构。安徽中航显示在变革过程中及时进行自我反思，勇于面对阻力，甚至作出了重大决策。其在实施变革方面的勇气和在克服阻力方面的智慧值得其他企业在战略转型中参考和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Organizational change is a phased process in which organizations purposefully and systematically alter their internal structures and behaviors in response to internal and external environmental changes, aiming to achieve a new equilibrium state and better fulfill organizational objectives. This case study illustrates the process of Anhui Aviation Industry Corporation Display Technology Co., Ltd. (AVIC) adapting to the unfavorable environment of continuous reduction in special equipment licensing policies through timely and strategic organizational changes. To meet the changing market demands, Anhui AVIC transformed its independent functional organizational structure into a cross-departmental matrix structure, enabling improved synergy. Subsequently, in order to unleash the employees&#39; initiative and creativity, they further evolved the matrix structure into a composite high-adaptability organizational structure. Throughout the change process, Anhui AVIC demonstrated the courage to reflect on its actions and overcome resistance, even making bold decisions. The company&#39;s courage in implementing change and its wisdom in overcoming obstacles are valuable references and lessons for enterprises undergoing strategic transformations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革的动因；组织变革的过程；组织变革的阻力；克服组织变革阻力的方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
